OrdersReviews_DF = pd.read_csv("olist_order_reviews_dataset.csv")

Products_DF = pd.read_csv("olist_products_dataset.csv")

ProductCategory_DF = pd.read_csv("product_category_name_translation.csv")

Payments_DF = pd.read_csv("olist_order_payments_dataset.csv")

# Criando uma matriz com o resumo dos datasets
datasets = [Customers_DF, Locations_DF, Orders_DF, OrderItems_DF, Payments_DF, OrdersReviews_DF, Products_DF, Sellers_DF,
            ProductCategory_DF]
names = ['olist_customer', 'olist_geolocation', 'olist_orders', 'olist_order_items', 'olist_order_payments',
         'olist_order_reviews', 'olist_products', 'olist_sellers', 'olist_products_category']

data_info = pd.DataFrame({})
data_info['dataset'] = names
data_info['n_rows'] = [df.shape[0] for df in datasets]
data_info['n_cols'] = [df.shape[1] for df in datasets]
data_info['columns'] = [list(df.columns) for df in datasets]
data_info['null_amount'] = [df.isnull().sum().sum() for df in datasets]
data_info['qty_null_columns'] = [len([col for col, null in df.isnull().sum().items() if null > 0]) for df in datasets]
data_info['null_columns'] = [', '.join([col for col, null in df.isnull().sum().items() if null > 0]) for df in datasets]

data_info.style.background_gradient()

names = ["boleto","credit_card","debit_card","voucher"]

# Vendas por UF do vendedor:
mean_df = df[['seller_state','payment_value']].groupby(by=["seller_state"], dropna=False).mean().reset_index()
count_df = df[['seller_state','payment_value']].groupby(by=["seller_state"], dropna=False).count().reset_index()
result = pd.merge(mean_df, count_df, how="inner", on="seller_state",suffixes=("_avg", "_count"))
result.sort_values('payment_value_count',ascending=False).reset_index(drop=True)

# Correlao entre a forma de pagamento e a UF do comprador (no h):
payment_type_df = pd.get_dummies(df.payment_type, prefix='payment_type')
customer_state_df = pd.get_dummies(df.customer_state, prefix='customer_state')
df_type_state = pd.concat([payment_type_df, customer_state_df],axis=1)
plt.figure(figsize=(30, 16))
sns.heatmap(df_type_state.corr(),annot= True,linewidths=0.5,fmt = ".1f")
plt.xticks(rotation=90)
plt.yticks(rotation=0)
plt.title('Correlation Map')
plt.show()
